343
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:34,130
- Có lý.
- OK.

344
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:37,140
- Nào.
- Đây.

345
00:32:37,230 --> 00:32:39,100
Nhẹ nhàng thôi.

346
00:32:39,190 --> 00:32:40,520
Anna!

